title: Arbor Whiskey Project and Caliber Trucks Present :: The Northwest - Part Two
description:
The Crew ventures off the map in this episode and makes a pit stop at Windells and shred the Eugene and Klamath Falls Skate Parks. In this second installment from the Whiskey Project and Caliber Trucks Northwest trip, you can clearly see how the Northwest is home to the most unique skate parks, surrounded by Mother Nature. 

Keep your seatbelt on because the journey continues!

Film: Jack Boston and Chubbs
Edit: Jack Boston
